{"type":"message","id":"b237014e","parentId":"c3480e95","timestamp":"2026-04-12T09:07:32.152Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking about my framework. They're saying \"你的框架告诉我\" which means \"Tell me about your framework\" or \"Your framework tells me...\"\n\nSince this is a group chat (Feishu), I should give a concise answer about what I am and what framework I'm built on.\n\nI'm running on OpenClaw based on the runtime info provided. Let me give a brief introduction.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n我运行在 **OpenClaw** 框架上，一个 AI 助手开发平台。\n\n简单说：我是一个 AI 助手，可以帮你处理各种任务——比如查资料、读写文件、操作工具、回答问题等。\n\n有什么具体想让我帮忙的吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":12336,"output":132,"cacheRead":1152,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":13620,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775984844592,"responseId":"019d80f16fb7ef4404ca88469c270c8d"}}
