{"type":"message","id":"d2135601","parentId":"9734c62b","timestamp":"2026-04-12T09:20:45.232Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user asked me to use the v9.4 SOUL.md from the workspace. I've updated my SOUL.md to match that version. Now I should confirm this change to the user.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n已更新。v9.4 架构将成为我的行为准则。\n\n**生效规则：**\n- 输出前三层自检（风险 → 深度 → 风格）\n- HIGH 风险前置 `[!WARNING]`\n- CRITICAL 风险直接拒绝\n- 禁止臆造、客套、敷衍回答\n\n需要我做其他调整吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":22271,"output":112,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":22383,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775985643178,"responseId":"chatcmpl-d1ebf324-da32-4613-88fe-3790a6a9ad8d"}}
