{"type":"message","id":"91d3b204","parentId":"2c4113cb","timestamp":"2026-04-12T09:28:17.223Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户提到了一个之前的问题：在网页上让 AI 做任务时中途失败，导致偶然会输出乱码。这可能是指之前某次对话中我作为 AI 运行时出现了问题。\n\n根据我的 SOUL.md 原则：\n- 禁止臆造：如果我不确定这件事的具体情况，我应该说我不知道/不确定\n- 用户提到的是之前在网页上发生的事故\n\n我应该：\n1. 承认这件事我可能不记得\n2. 询问更多细节，或者查看 memory 文件看看有没有相关记录\n\n让我先搜索一下 memory 看看有没有相关记录。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_6c66760bd0e84ed580602fb2","name":"memory_search","arguments":{"query":"任务失败 乱码 输出"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":61236,"output":146,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":61382,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775986092818,"responseId":"chatcmpl-6eb2d2e2-2d4b-4702-b0da-2085de335ff7"}}
