{"type":"message","id":"9f3b6cdb","parentId":"36d0a29c","timestamp":"2026-04-12T09:31:47.297Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I don't see today's logs. This was likely a different session (web interface) that isn't logged in the current workspace. Let me also check if there's an error log somewhere in the system related to OpenClaw.\n\nSince I can't find the specific incident, let me provide some general analysis about what could cause this and potential fixes based on my knowledge of the codebase.\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n我没有找到相关日志。这个问题可能发生在 web 界面的独立会话中，未写入当前工作区。\n\n---\n\n## 乱码问题分析\n\n根据代码审查，潜在原因：\n\n### 1. 流式输出截断\n```javascript\n// stream 处理可能在高延迟时断裂\n// channel-streaming-Z0N1qOcY.js\n```\n\n### 2. Unicode 处理问题\n- 表情符号/特殊字符可能在某些渠道截断\n- 编码不匹配导致乱码\n\n### 3. 上下文溢出\n- 长任务耗尽 context window\n- 模型输出被强制截断\n\n---\n\n## 建议的临时解决方案\n\n| 方法 | 说明 |\n|------|------|\n| **重启 Gateway** | `openclaw gateway restart` |\n| **清理会话** | 关闭并重新打开 web 页面 |\n| **简化任务** | 将大任务拆分为小步骤 |\n\n---\n\n如果你能提供乱码的截图或具体文本，我可以更准确定位问题。或者你可以尝试复现，我在这里观察日志。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":64237,"output":289,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":64526,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775986280823,"responseId":"chatcmpl-0dc18129-5313-40ac-94dd-58fd550f1a14"}}
