{"type":"message","id":"0c696093","parentId":"3a72d083","timestamp":"2026-04-12T09:57:20.152Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"v8 已经在运行。让我检查 scene-classifier 的状态。它可能在不同的端口运行，或者没有运行。\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n**v8 已经在运行：**\n\n```\n端口 3103: v8.0 ✓\n队列状态: 17 个任务, 2 完成, 15 失败\n内存: 23.3% 使用\n```\n\n---\n\n**scene-classifier 没有运行。** 需要启动吗？\n\n---\n\n## 同时运行？是的，可以\n\n| 服务 | 端口 | 关系 |\n|------|------|------|\n| **v8** | 3103 | 任务编排系统 |\n| **scene-classifier** | 5003 (默认) | 场景分类（可独立） |\n| **Gateway** | 3102 | 对外接口 |\n\n它们是**独立服务**，可以同时运行：\n- v8 负责执行任务\n- scene-classifier 负责场景判断和硬拦截\n\n---\n\n要启动 scene-classifier 吗？在你的终端执行：\n\n```bash\ncd ~/.openclaw/v8/scene-classifier\nsource venv/bin/activate\npython api_server.py\n```"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":106244,"output":229,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":106473,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775987834199,"responseId":"chatcmpl-3199027c-ba26-49af-a1ea-8d023bef21b9"}}
