{"type":"message","id":"59d2ac8e","parentId":"5c41d68e","timestamp":"2026-04-12T09:58:23.367Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking about how their messages flow through the system. Let me explain the architecture of how a message gets processed in OpenClaw.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n## 消息 flow（你的信息怎么走的）\n\n```\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│                      你 (Web/APP)                           │\n└─────────────────────────┬───────────────────────────────────┘\n                          │\n                          ▼\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│                   Gateway (3102)                           │\n│  - 接收消息                                                 │\n│  - 权限验证                                                 │\n│  - 会话管理                                                 │\n└─────────────────────────┬───────────────────────────────────┘\n                          │\n                          ▼\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│              Scene Classifier (5003) [如果开启]            │\n│  - 场景判断 (task/chat)                                     │\n│  - CRITICAL 硬拦截                                          │\n│  - 模板注入                                                 │\n└─────────────────────────┬───────────────────────────────────┘\n                          │\n                          ▼\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│                   v8 (3103) - 任务编排                      │\n│  - 评分引擎 (6因子 → 策略选择)                              │\n│  - 任务调度                                                 │\n│  - 执行器分配                                               │\n└─────────────────────────┬───────────────────────────────────┘\n                          │\n              ┌───────────┴───────────┐\n              ▼                       ▼\n        ┌─────────┐            ┌─────────────┐\n        │ DIRECT  │            │ SUBAGENT    │\n        │ 直接执行 │            │  spawn 子代理│\n        └────┬────┘            └──────┬──────┘\n             │                        │\n             ▼                        ▼\n        ┌──────────────────────────────┐\n        │         LLM (模型)           │\n        │   生成回复                    │\n        └─────────────┬────────────────┘\n                      │\n                      ▼\n        ┌──────────────────────────────┐\n        │   文本净化层                  │\n        │   - stripModelSpecialTokens  │\n        │   - stripReasoningTags       │\n        │   - sanitizeForPlainText    │\n        └─────────────┬────────────────┘\n                      │\n                      ▼\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│                    返回给你                                 │\n└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n```\n\n---\n\n**当前状态：**\n- ✅ Gateway (3102) — 运行中\n- ✅ v8 (3103) — 运行中\n- ❌ Scene Classifier (5003) — **未启动**\n\n---\n\n你说的乱码问题，**可能的位置：**\n1. **LLM 输出** → 模型本身问题\n2. **流式截断** → 网络波动\n3. **exec 输出** → 命令输出未净化（最可能）"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":2392,"output":570,"cacheRead":104192,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":107154,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775987871367,"responseId":"019d81204776203bb39655f1c25c1284"}}
