{"type":"message","id":"ffd667e4","parentId":"61a72202","timestamp":"2026-04-12T10:04:19.997Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b5282acd1f8acc49ae03d4b373fc\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_f078a2787ee791cfa7b974fd499fd49f\",\n  \"conversation_label\": \"oc_1b955e738aa196d7f2afe9e1c1d35575\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_f078a2787ee791cfa7b974fd499fd49f\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sun 2026-04-12 18:04 GMT+8\",\n  \"group_subject\": \"oc_1b955e738aa196d7f2afe9e1c1d35575\",\n  \"is_group_chat\": true\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_f078a2787ee791cfa7b974fd499fd49f\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_f078a2787ee791cfa7b974fd499fd49f\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_f078a2787ee791cfa7b974fd499fd49f\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b5282acd1f8acc49ae03d4b373fc]\nou_f078a2787ee791cfa7b974fd499fd49f: 怎么解决呢"}],"timestamp":1775988259993}}
{"type":"message","id":"ef857f00","parentId":"ffd667e4","timestamp":"2026-04-12T10:04:26.373Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户问乱码问题怎么解决。根据我之前的分析，最可能的原因是 exec 输出没有净化。我需要给出实际的解决方案。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n## 乱码问题解决方案\n\n### 方案 1：启动 Scene Classifier（推荐）\n\n在你的终端执行：\n\n```bash\ncd ~/.openclaw/v8/scene-classifier\nsource venv/bin/activate\npython api_server.py &\n```\n\n然后在配置中启用它。\n\n---\n\n### 方案 2：避免触发 exec（临时）\n\n**乱码最可能是 exec 命令输出导致的。**\n\n以后避免让 AI：\n- 执行 `ls`、`cat`、`grep` 等命令\n- 读取大文件\n- 执行任何 shell 命令\n\n---\n\n### 方案 3：官方修复（长期）\n\n给 OpenClaw 提 issue：\n- 位置：`exec-BLYxAGIO.js` 第 293、297 行\n- 问题：exec 输出没有净化\n- 修复：添加 `.toString()` 前验证编码\n\n---\n\n### 方案 4：自己打补丁\n\n在你的 OpenClaw 源码里找到 `exec-BLYxAGIO.js`，把：\n\n```javascript\nstdout += d.toString();\n```\n\n改成：\n\n```javascript\n// 净化输出，过滤控制字符\nconst sanitized = d.toString().replace(/[\\x00-\\x08\\x0B\\x0C\\x0E-\\x1F\\x7F]/g, '');\nstdout += sanitized;\n```\n\n---\n\n**你现在能做的：**\n1. 先试试方案 1（启动分类器）\n2. 以后避免让 AI 执行命令\n\n选哪个？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":107402,"output":325,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":107727,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775988260003,"responseId":"chatcmpl-9ddd0413-d405-4ff2-8f2a-c77645310b3b"}}
