{"type":"message","id":"3e67e7b1","parentId":"1cc43ca6","timestamp":"2026-04-12T10:29:10.427Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"让我检查一下Gateway的进程，看看它是如何连接到v8和scene-classifier的。\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n根据我的检查，**目前没有自动经过评分和分类**。\n\n---\n\n## 原因\n\n你的 `config.json` 中**没有配置** v8 和 scene-classifier 的连接：\n\n```json\n// 缺失的配置\n{\n  \"v8\": { \"url\": \"http://127.0.0.1:3103\" },\n  \"sceneClassifier\": { \"url\": \"http://127.0.0.1:3104\" }\n}\n```\n\n虽然这两个服务在运行，但 Gateway 不知道它们的存在。\n\n---\n\n## 消息流程（当前）\n\n```\n你 → Gateway (3102) → 直接到 LLM\n```\n\n---\n\n## 想要启用评分和分类？\n\n需要在 config.json 中添加：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"scoring\": {\n    \"enabled\": true,\n    \"v8Url\": \"http://127.0.0.1:3103\"\n  },\n  \"sceneClassifier\": {\n    \"enabled\": true,\n    \"url\": \"http://127.0.0.1:3104\"\n  }\n}\n```\n\n然后重启 Gateway。\n\n---\n\n**要启用吗？**"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":114288,"output":251,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":114539,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775989745589,"responseId":"chatcmpl-daaad399-2986-40d7-b1b2-c86d3fb9b2e5"}}
